Peltier Says U.S. Housing Recovery Will Begin in 2012

-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-13T19:07:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/peltier-says-u-s-housing-recovery-will-begin-in-2012-video-.html
Ron Peltier, chief executive officer
of HomeServices of America Inc., talks about the outlook for the
U.S. housing market.  Peltier, speaking with  Matt Miller  on Bloomberg 
Television's "Fast Forward," says a recovery will begin by late 
2012 building on a "pent-up demand" for homeownership. (Source: 
Bloomberg)  Running time 04:12
 